tuation/Question</span><hr size=1> Last night, a friend and I were in DL, tracked the Patriarch (who can drop either the Giant Sized Monocle for the Warrior Epic or a Treeweave), and proceeded to work our dot's on him.  Being two druids, we had it made... it was only a matter of time. We had a big open area, where nothing wanders, and very few people venture.... nice and quiet and undisturbed. <br>
<br>
The Pat gets right at halfway down, and I notice someone walking near the pat.  As soon as I tell my friend &quot;We have company&quot;, the person proceeds to engage the Pat.  (Who is obviously already taken)  As this person continues to get the crap beaten out of him, my friend /shouts that the pat is taken, just as two more people show up.  They don't back off.  I nuke the pat a couple of times, just for good measure on our side.. and within a short time he dies.... we get the experience, and I quickly loot up and get a Monocle, that I give to my friend.<br>
<br>
