<br>
But my question is:  If someone ever OBVIOUSLY attempts to KS you, and then wants to buy the looted items, what is your response?<br>
<br>
Personally, I had a few choice words that I kept under my belt, but I told my friend he should double the price for the jerk... hehehe<br>
<br>
